originalText.text:
Apartment Jeannie and her entire team were just what I needed and more. All of the team members were engaging and thoughtful and paid attention to my needs. They helped organize my apt in ways that I would never have thought of on my own and helped transform my apt into a home. For me this was a therapeutic experience, helping me to transition to a new stage in life.  The designers/ organizers Nick, Jessica, Lisa, Lisa, Erin and the Handiman who put furniture together all are the best at what they do. They were also always mindful of my budget, for which I am grateful and they always made me feel really good about the org and design decisions being made collaboratively.

Jeannie is the absolute best as well.  She took the time to help me organize old family pictures that I had no clue how to display. I now have a family photo wall and art displayed in bookcases that honors my family very well. You will love working with apartment Jeanie and her team. I highly recommend them.

originalText.text: I couldn’t be happier with my experience with ApartmentJeanie. I just moved from my hometown of Nashville to New York and not only did Jeanie and her team make me feel welcomed to the city by sharing NYC tips, the unpacking/organization services took my little studio from being an apartment to being a home. Lisa was one of my organizers and she kept me informed the whole day as she worked in my apt. She then sent a synopsis email that had links of suggested items to get, next steps for me to complete, and even a couple reminders for me of things I’d mentioned I wanted to get done for the apt and my move. I was blown away. 10/10 experience!

originalText.text: I had a fantastic experience using apartmentjeanie’s services for my apartment!  The staff is friendly, conscientious, and communicative.  The team maximized the space in my apartment with furniture I already own, and I’m amazed at how organized my closets and storage spaces are!  Lisa was fabulous to work with and gave me great decor ideas as well. I highly recommend their services!

I can’t say enough about the incredible team at Apt Jeanie! They helped me move in and get settled into my new apartment and I absolutely love it. They did everything from organize my closets to style my apartment and source needed items and even helped me sell the furniture I no longer wanted.

They were a dream to work - their skills and network are top notch AND they are a joy to work with - and I recommend them to everyone I know.

originalText.text: I have known Jeanie for years now, and she is hands-down the best professional organizer in New York City and Charleston, SC. She is an expert in home organization and move management. Moving homes is one of life's most painful processes, and Jeanie helps you to cross that process as painlessly as possible and even enjoy the journey.  I've learned a lot from her which carries over to different organizational skills in my personal and professional life. She has very high standards, is super professional, and has keen attention to detail which shows in the wonderful spaces she produces that tie up to your personal goals and lifestyle. I cannot recommend her highly enough and will put her on a pedestal as one of NYC's top professional organizers in home organization and movement management.
